==Translingual==

===Alternative forms===
* In Taiwan and Hong Kong, the component above <big>{{l|mul|蒦}}</big> is written with <span style="font-size:large;">[[⻀]]</span> (ram's horn component), which is the orthodox form found in the {{w|Shuowen Jiezi}} ({{lw|zh|說文解字}}).
* In mainland China (based on {{w|Xin Zixing}}, {{lw|zh|新字形}}), Japanese {{w|kanji}}, Korean {{w|hanja}} and Vietnamese {{w|History of writing in Vietnam|Nôm}}, the component above <big>{{l|mul|蒦}}</big> is written with <span style="font-size:large;">{{l|mul|艹}}</span> (grass radical), which is based on the {{w|Kangxi dictionary}}.

